{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC16_RAN_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x29,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hello, Ranun."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Ayesha. You're as energetic as always."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x4e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I feel like I get energized just from looking at you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "You're probably blessed by the<CR>god of the sun and smiles."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I-Is that so? I'm not really sure..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, Ranun, are you performing your music here today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "No. I'm waiting for the wind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, the wind...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Have you ever questioned it?<CR>About where the wind that runs<CR>throughout the world is going?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "No, I've never thought about that. Ranun, do you know the answer?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yes. The wind is...running toward the person that should receive it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "The wind blows in the direction of a certain person, for a certain moment, at a certain place, who shall receive it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Th-That sounds so complicated.<CR>I don't think I really understand..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, I was hoping to hear your music..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I feel honored. However, I never thought that you'd be the person to say that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, you and I might be on a matching wavelength..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "But, I can't today. Currently, I've lost sight of the sound..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "The sound...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "If you don't continuously have new inspirations, you cannot create the sounds."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I want you to recall the story I just told you about. Remember the story about the wind?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "The wind will bring new sounds with it. That is why I'm waiting here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "The wind is essential for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "(...Music is so complicated.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x51,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Haha, although it is a bit boring. However, endurance is required to play music."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x54,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "But just waiting is...how should I say...making me hungry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "That's not surprising. I feel like it's such a waste of time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Why don't you try working or something while you wait?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x157,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "W...or...k...ing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I-Is something wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x159,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, you have an interesting idea. Yes...very interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(R-Really...?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "But I have a very weak relationship with that word."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe6,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I appreciate your advice, but I think I'll choose to go with my own plan."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I'll wait for the time when the wind will carry new sounds to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "(Th-That kinda seems cool, but it also kinda doesn't...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "I mean, if not today, then there's always tomorrow. If not tomorrow, then there's always the day after tomorrow."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "The promised day will come after overcoming many hardships."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "But I feel like you're not overcoming anything... Nope, nothing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "The new sounds are right around the corner. Yes, they have to be there..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "However, even so...I'm getting hungry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "(I wonder why my head starts to hurt every time I talk to Ranun...)"
        }
    ]
}